lead_paragraph: "Downton Abbey" said goodbye to an estimated 9.6 million viewers on Sunday night, lowering the curtain on PBS' most successful series in ages with its fourth most-watched episode.

headline.main: 'Downton Abbey' Ends Run Before 9.6 Million Viewers
